-- Cementos Argos Says Colombia Regulator Approves Spin Off
-- B y   C h r i s t i n e   J e n k i n s
-- 2012-04-27T21:50:22Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-04-27/cementos-argos-says-colombia-regulator-approves-spin-off.html
Colombia’s financial regulator has
approved  Cementos Argos SA (CEMARGOS) ’s spin off of assets that aren’t
related to cement production, including portfolio investments,
real estate and port assets, to owner Inversiones Argos, the
company said in a filing.  To contact the reporter on this story:
